      "Monitoring: Alerting rules for disk >70%, CPU >80%, P99 >500ms, replication lag >5s"
    ],
    "patterns_to_follow": "Use CREATE INDEX CONCURRENTLY to avoid locking production tables. Test partition migration on a staging copy of production data first. Route reads at the application layer using a connection wrapper that directs queries by type (write → primary, search/aggregation → replica). Use feature flags to gradually shift read traffic to replicas.",
